    "description": {
      "chat": "",
      "gmnotes": "",
      "short": "",
      "value": "<p>You are at ease in the wilderness, able to navigate treacherous terrain, and capable of recognizing flora and fauna. You gain the @Compendium[sfrpg.feats.seWKgVZbtyOPhl6e]{Nimble Moves (Combat)} feat. If you already have the Nimble Moves feat, you gain an additional combat feat of your choice for which you qualify. Further, you can use Survival in place of Life Science to identify creatures of the plant, animal, and vermin types, and you gain a +1 insight bonus to Survival checks. This bonus increases by 1 at 5th level and every four levels afterward to a maximum of +5 at 17th level.</p>",
